name: WiR/Autonomy @ Skydio
description:
Come by for a fun- filled evening of networking, Skydio drone demos & some tech talk from your sisters in engineering. Our panelists will include:
  • Kristen Holtz - Skydio - Head of Tracking & Cinematics
  • Heart Hsin - Skydio - Sr Hardware Engineering Program Manager
  • Snigdha Bommadevara - Skydio - Sr Electronics Design Engineer
  • Blythe Towal - Saildrone - VP of SW/Head of Machine Learning
  • Becky Soltanian - Sanborn - VP of R&D
  • Nika Carlson - Scale AI/Cruise - Former Chief of Staff & Head of Design
